== Kinki Region == * {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Ise)|en|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Ise City, Mie Prefecture, under the jurisdiction of the {{ill|Inner Shrine|en}} . * {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Kihoku)|en|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Jinai, Kiho Town, Minami-Muro District, Mie Prefecture.
== Chugoku Region == * {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Okayama)|en}} - Located in Kita Ward, Okayama City, Okayama Prefecture. A subordinate shrine of {{ill|Kibitsu Shrine|en|12=draft|12=draft}} . == See Also == * {{ill|Komori Shrine|en}}
