'''Sakurai Koyasu Shrine''' (櫻井子安神社) is a [[Shinto shrine]] located in [[:en:Asahi, Chiba|Asahi, Chiba]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]], Japan.

